WEBVTT

00:12.850 --> 00:18.280
[2010]

00:26.230 --> 00:27.760
Professor Geng came over a few days ago.

00:27.760 --> 00:28.320
Prof.

00:29.160 --> 00:29.620
Come in.

00:31.350 --> 00:31.810
Come in.

00:38.390 --> 00:40.450
These files have been reclassified.

00:41.200 --> 00:42.430
These are the research notes.

00:42.430 --> 00:43.220
All questionable items

00:43.220 --> 00:44.220
have been marked.

00:44.320 --> 00:45.380
Please have a look.

00:47.110 --> 00:48.840
I have read the book you gave me.

00:48.880 --> 00:50.480
These are the reading notes.

00:50.520 --> 00:51.720
Okay, put them there.

00:53.560 --> 00:54.520
Go back early.

01:09.280 --> 01:10.350
Is this

01:10.700 --> 01:13.030
the Jiang Hansheng you mentioned before?

01:16.280 --> 01:17.200
Jealous?

01:21.950 --> 01:23.840
Having such a remarkable student

01:24.710 --> 01:25.710
is a rare blessing

01:26.200 --> 01:28.230
in my life.

01:29.940 --> 01:30.940
But he

01:31.640 --> 01:32.590
has a weakness,

01:33.000 --> 01:34.600
too eager for quick success.

01:35.680 --> 01:36.479
Why is that?

01:37.400 --> 01:38.420
Ever since he got

01:38.450 --> 01:40.590
the authority
to handle cases independently,

01:40.590 --> 01:42.560
he has accepted all kinds of cases.

01:43.229 --> 01:44.400
He works desperately.

01:44.400 --> 01:45.070
To himself,

01:45.590 --> 01:46.520
and to the enemy,

01:47.150 --> 01:49.000
he keeps

01:49.000 --> 01:50.330
a hidden ruthlessness.

01:51.479 --> 01:52.789
That ruthlessness

01:53.350 --> 01:54.870
makes me

01:55.430 --> 01:56.710
worried.

01:58.759 --> 01:59.920
Why is it like this?

01:59.950 --> 02:00.760
I asked him

02:01.580 --> 02:02.780
why he works

02:02.810 --> 02:03.920
so desperately.

02:05.840 --> 02:07.510
Was he for the truth

02:08.560 --> 02:09.360
or for credit?

02:10.120 --> 02:11.710
Do you know what he said?

02:12.030 --> 02:12.890
For promotion?

02:17.470 --> 02:18.590
He said

02:18.680 --> 02:19.800
he did so

02:20.400 --> 02:22.470
to fulfill a wish.

02:31.350 --> 02:31.950
Senior,

02:32.310 --> 02:33.190
I know you well.

02:34.150 --> 02:35.810
You have a broad perspective.

02:35.829 --> 02:37.010
You must be unsatisfied

02:37.010 --> 02:38.180
with his answer.

02:40.240 --> 02:41.360
Frankly speaking,

02:41.870 --> 02:43.240
his

02:43.840 --> 02:45.310
edge

02:46.360 --> 02:47.190
and ability

02:47.680 --> 02:48.590
are top-notch.

02:49.750 --> 02:50.880
But his personality

02:52.310 --> 02:53.370
is not good enough.

02:55.750 --> 02:57.000
Don't jump the gun.

02:58.370 --> 03:00.300
Wait until something big happens.

03:00.840 --> 03:01.700
Then we'll see.

04:21.100 --> 04:26.710
[Sunsets Secrets Regrets]

04:27.110 --> 04:29.470
[Episode 11]

04:30.390 --> 04:31.120
He's gone.

04:31.160 --> 04:32.230
We found his phone

04:32.250 --> 04:34.310
and the tracker on his boutonniere
in the car.

04:34.310 --> 04:34.950
What?

04:34.950 --> 04:36.070
He's gone?

04:36.390 --> 04:37.950
How could he be gone?

04:41.480 --> 04:43.270
But the one who showed up
that day wasn't Qi Yan.

04:43.270 --> 04:44.600
It was his subordinate.

04:45.030 --> 04:46.000
Yao Weihai

04:46.040 --> 04:48.070
didn't give an order in time

04:48.070 --> 04:49.310
to rescue Hansheng.

04:49.800 --> 04:50.750
That was the only chance to catch

04:50.750 --> 04:53.190
the crime syndicate of the 8/17 Case.

04:53.630 --> 04:54.830
If we missed it,

04:55.510 --> 04:57.840
all our previous efforts would be in vain.

04:57.950 --> 04:59.430
He must make

04:59.430 --> 05:02.030
a choice that benefits
the overall situation.

05:02.320 --> 05:03.690
I know it.

05:04.620 --> 05:05.610
But…

05:07.160 --> 05:09.560
It's about to pass the golden 72 hours.

05:10.450 --> 05:11.570
If we still can't find…

05:11.570 --> 05:12.430
Yao Weihai!

05:22.190 --> 05:24.720
Leader Yao, then we will go look
for him first.

05:32.040 --> 05:32.600
Senior,

05:33.240 --> 05:34.040
it's my fault.

05:36.870 --> 05:37.680
Where is he?

05:39.680 --> 05:40.360
Where is he?

05:43.560 --> 05:45.270
Give my student back.

05:45.870 --> 05:46.930
Give him back to me.

05:48.350 --> 05:50.080
Give him back!

05:53.010 --> 05:54.870
We've been trying our best
to look for him.

05:54.870 --> 05:55.950
Did you find him?

05:57.430 --> 05:59.390
How did you promise me back then?

05:59.390 --> 06:00.270
You said you would

06:00.270 --> 06:02.390
guarantee his safety.

06:02.490 --> 06:03.340
Where is he?

06:03.680 --> 06:05.270
Tell me, where is he?

06:09.390 --> 06:10.310
I'm sorry.

06:15.070 --> 06:17.270
You bastard!

06:27.430 --> 06:28.890
Where is the pocket watch?

06:29.160 --> 06:31.040
Did he have the pocket watch with him?

06:31.040 --> 06:32.100
What pocket watch?

06:37.440 --> 06:42.210
[The sixth day
after Jiang Hansheng was kidnapped]

07:52.630 --> 07:54.030
What are you waiting for?

07:56.310 --> 07:58.370
Waiting for your friends to save you?

07:59.760 --> 08:01.000
They won't be here.

08:02.630 --> 08:04.630
They can't find this place at all.

08:08.680 --> 08:10.120
They abandoned you.

08:11.510 --> 08:13.370
Officer Jiang, have you realized

08:13.750 --> 08:15.190
who your real friend is?

08:20.270 --> 08:20.920
Me.

08:22.040 --> 08:23.430
I am your real friend.

08:25.560 --> 08:27.490
As long as you accept me as a friend,

08:31.040 --> 08:31.820
just say,

08:32.870 --> 08:34.150
"I am your friend",

08:36.030 --> 08:38.390
and I will let you die comfortably.

08:43.659 --> 08:46.190
The tracker of the pocket watch
is activated.

08:48.150 --> 08:48.680
Let’s go!

08:57.320 --> 08:58.640
Give me the pocket watch.

08:58.640 --> 09:00.040
Give me the pocket watch.

09:03.870 --> 09:04.730
Officer Jiang.

09:05.840 --> 09:07.670
Jiang Hansheng,

09:08.740 --> 09:10.340
I changed my mind.

09:11.390 --> 09:13.240
I won't let you die.

09:15.200 --> 09:17.960
I will make your life a living hell.

09:20.510 --> 09:21.510
What do you want?

09:22.840 --> 09:24.040
You want this, right?

09:24.600 --> 09:25.800
You want this, right?

09:26.390 --> 09:27.200
You want it?

09:27.920 --> 09:28.760
You want her?

09:29.240 --> 09:31.000
You want your girl, right?

09:34.270 --> 09:35.550
You will never

09:37.950 --> 09:39.640
get her.

09:54.080 --> 09:54.750
Six days.

09:56.790 --> 09:58.120
After a full six days,

09:59.790 --> 10:02.630
Yao Weihai finally found

10:03.480 --> 10:05.120
Hansheng in an abandoned warehouse.

10:05.120 --> 10:07.380
When he was sent into the operating room,

10:08.320 --> 10:09.630
the doctors told me

10:10.600 --> 10:11.960
that multiple organs

10:12.610 --> 10:13.360
in his body

10:13.380 --> 10:15.780
were already showing signs of failure.

10:17.510 --> 10:19.840
They let me brace myself.

10:21.790 --> 10:23.750
He never mentioned

10:23.750 --> 10:26.000
how he survived those six days.

10:27.360 --> 10:28.390
I have no idea.

10:30.510 --> 10:32.200
What I do know is that

10:33.120 --> 10:35.780
although Hansheng received
an award and praise

10:36.000 --> 10:37.510
for this arrest,

10:39.600 --> 10:42.940
his treatment lasted for a full two years.

11:23.120 --> 11:23.910
What's up?

11:27.440 --> 11:28.910
Can you help me dry my hair?

12:31.870 --> 12:33.200
What are you looking at?

12:34.510 --> 12:35.270
You.

13:13.080 --> 13:14.680
Do you have something to say?

13:23.670 --> 13:24.790
Is your name

13:27.480 --> 13:28.720
Jiang Hansheng?

13:31.390 --> 13:32.150
Yes, it is.

13:40.420 --> 13:42.280
You wouldn't lie to me, would you?

13:48.750 --> 13:49.810
I didn't lie to you.

13:52.240 --> 13:53.770
Did you really not lie to me?

13:57.550 --> 13:59.220
Then what about

14:00.550 --> 14:02.030
a close call

14:04.720 --> 14:06.030
you told me?

14:12.000 --> 14:12.930
Jiang Hansheng.

14:14.390 --> 14:15.030
Why?

14:16.600 --> 14:18.130
Those things five years ago

14:19.600 --> 14:21.790
have nothing to do with you.

14:24.480 --> 14:25.840
Why did you do that?

14:31.750 --> 14:32.960
Did Prof...

14:42.870 --> 14:43.800
Jiang Hansheng.

14:46.790 --> 14:47.600
Why?

14:50.790 --> 14:51.440
Zhou Jin,

14:52.710 --> 14:54.000
that’s my job.

14:54.720 --> 14:56.320
It has nothing to do with you.

14:57.030 --> 14:57.830
You're lying.

15:00.480 --> 15:01.320
At that time,

15:03.630 --> 15:05.240
I didn't even remember you.

15:13.200 --> 15:13.960
Don't cry.

15:20.750 --> 15:21.790
Do you like me?

15:24.000 --> 15:24.840
Yes.

15:26.910 --> 15:28.550
Since when?

15:32.200 --> 15:32.870
Zhou Jin,

15:34.150 --> 15:34.750
I love you.

15:38.080 --> 15:39.480
When I first met you,

15:41.150 --> 15:42.280
I wanted to have you.

16:39.360 --> 16:40.240
You're late.

16:42.320 --> 16:44.920
I had to deal with something
before coming out.

16:45.630 --> 16:47.030
How long do I have to wait?

16:47.360 --> 16:48.840
What do you mean? Are you rushing me?

16:48.840 --> 16:49.550
Sir.

16:49.630 --> 16:50.550
It's been five years.

16:50.550 --> 16:51.790
Can't I rush you?

16:51.820 --> 16:52.840
I haven't even scolded you yet.

16:52.840 --> 16:53.840
Do you know why I'm late?

16:53.840 --> 16:54.840
Why should I care?

16:55.510 --> 16:56.840
Is Heipi your man?

16:57.910 --> 16:59.000
He was beaten badly

16:59.120 --> 17:01.120
and thrown at the door
of the narcotics team.

17:01.120 --> 17:02.580
He kept calling for Cheng.

17:02.960 --> 17:04.329
If I weren't there for a meeting,

17:04.329 --> 17:06.460
you'd have another mess on your hands.

17:07.000 --> 17:08.349
He has nothing to do with me.

17:08.349 --> 17:09.550
He has nothing to do with you?

17:09.550 --> 17:10.500
What about Huang Song?

17:10.500 --> 17:11.810
What about Lai San?

17:11.829 --> 17:12.869
Get it straight.

17:12.920 --> 17:14.650
It's Lai San's own crime of killing a man.

17:14.650 --> 17:15.910
I asked Huang Song to help him
dispose of the body

17:15.910 --> 17:17.970
so that you guys could find it sooner.

17:18.349 --> 17:19.480
Why are you yelling?

17:23.400 --> 17:25.130
When will Lai San be sentenced?

17:25.440 --> 17:26.170
I don't know.

17:38.270 --> 17:39.960
He has the gun you handed in.

17:40.400 --> 17:42.150
He'll be sentenced sooner or later.

17:42.150 --> 17:43.550
He has been involved in other cases.

17:43.550 --> 17:45.550
They have to be dealt with together.

17:46.160 --> 17:47.830
What did you explain about the gun?

17:47.830 --> 17:49.160
Fished it out of the sea.

17:49.550 --> 17:50.270
Awesome.

17:50.880 --> 17:52.790
You guys went into the sea
to fish out a gun.

17:52.790 --> 17:54.520
Your subordinate, Huang Song,

17:54.960 --> 17:56.890
might have to serve a few years too.

17:57.340 --> 17:59.470
He stole drugs and sold them secretly,

18:00.400 --> 18:02.080
breaking the rules of the gang.

18:02.080 --> 18:03.110
By going to prison,

18:03.110 --> 18:04.440
he gets to keep his life.

18:08.310 --> 18:09.160
How about you?

18:11.480 --> 18:12.030
Me?

18:12.030 --> 18:12.630
Of course.

18:12.830 --> 18:13.760
I want to go home.

18:13.790 --> 18:14.920
Will you approve it?

18:17.440 --> 18:17.970
Alright.

18:17.990 --> 18:18.790
Just kidding.

18:24.310 --> 18:25.400
Did Zhou Jin and Jiang Hansheng

18:25.400 --> 18:27.400
cause any trouble for you recently?

18:27.600 --> 18:29.510
As the ex, I'm the trouble itself.

18:31.920 --> 18:32.870
As you said,

18:33.330 --> 18:35.660
I transferred her away from the 8/17 Case.

18:35.830 --> 18:37.350
She must be furious.

18:37.920 --> 18:38.720
She has already

18:38.720 --> 18:40.450
cut you into pieces in her mind.

18:40.870 --> 18:41.760
I don't care,

18:41.790 --> 18:43.450
as long as you're okay with it.

18:49.400 --> 18:49.930
Alright.

18:50.160 --> 18:51.360
Let's talk business.

18:52.270 --> 18:53.720
They will restock soon,

18:53.720 --> 18:55.640
transporting a large batch of meth
from the Jin-Hai Line.

18:55.640 --> 18:56.680
He Wu is taking it very seriously.

18:56.680 --> 18:57.960
It must be a big deal.

19:00.750 --> 19:01.610
Time and place?

19:02.000 --> 19:03.060
Not confirmed yet.

19:03.830 --> 19:04.440
However,

19:04.460 --> 19:06.740
it's said that Old Scorpion
will personally supervise this time.

19:06.740 --> 19:08.800
So, they are acting very cautiously.

19:10.270 --> 19:12.400
Find a way to get close to Old Scorpion.

19:12.830 --> 19:13.880
He Wu will definitely

19:13.880 --> 19:15.140
be short of hands then.

19:15.160 --> 19:16.110
Without Lai San,

19:16.310 --> 19:17.750
I am confident I can make him choose me.

19:17.750 --> 19:18.550
It has to be me.

19:23.830 --> 19:25.030
It's been five years.

19:25.440 --> 19:27.470
We finally got the business

19:27.510 --> 19:28.640
of the Jin-Hai Line.

19:29.590 --> 19:32.120
Old Scorpion has been hiding
for so many years

19:32.310 --> 19:33.710
and has finally shown up.

19:34.270 --> 19:34.920
Yes.

19:36.350 --> 19:37.830
This is our only chance.

19:39.000 --> 19:39.920
After this,

19:40.590 --> 19:41.720
I can go home.

19:43.480 --> 19:44.610
Does He Wu trust you?

19:47.880 --> 19:48.920
Don't worry about that.

19:48.920 --> 19:49.920
I have my own ways.

19:50.920 --> 19:52.120
Jiang Cheng, listen,

19:52.680 --> 19:53.540
don't do anything out of bounds

19:53.540 --> 19:55.060
to get promoted.

19:56.550 --> 19:57.350
Out of bounds?

19:57.750 --> 19:59.200
Tell me, what are the bounds?

19:59.200 --> 20:00.040
Where are they?

20:00.040 --> 20:02.040
What does it mean to be out of bounds?

20:18.960 --> 20:20.560
What are you doing? Defiant?

20:20.920 --> 20:22.790
Yes, I don't buy it.

20:23.790 --> 20:24.270
Yao.

20:25.230 --> 20:25.960
Look at this.

20:26.030 --> 20:26.990
During the last deal,

20:26.990 --> 20:28.420
I was shot by our man.

20:28.590 --> 20:30.250
I almost died in the hospital.

20:30.550 --> 20:31.170
And here.

20:31.680 --> 20:32.880
When I was in prison,

20:32.880 --> 20:33.880
I got slashed.

20:34.200 --> 20:34.830
And here.

20:35.160 --> 20:35.830
Look.

20:36.230 --> 20:37.210
I have more scars.

20:37.210 --> 20:39.010
Do you want to see them one by one?

20:39.200 --> 20:39.830
Tell me,

20:39.830 --> 20:41.560
at what time was I out of bounds?

20:44.960 --> 20:46.710
I had no parents since I was young.

20:46.710 --> 20:48.280
The Zhou family raised me.

20:48.750 --> 20:51.150
They are the ones
who care about me the most.

20:51.630 --> 20:53.250
Every time I couldn't hold on,

20:53.250 --> 20:54.310
as long as I thought of them,

20:54.310 --> 20:55.680
thought of my family waiting
for me at home,

20:55.680 --> 20:56.880
I didn't even dare to die.

20:56.880 --> 20:58.010
I could only hold on.

20:58.310 --> 20:59.030
But now?

20:59.800 --> 21:00.480
Yao, tell me,

21:00.480 --> 21:01.790
what have I become?

21:03.960 --> 21:04.820
How about this?

21:06.000 --> 21:06.860
You take the gun

21:06.920 --> 21:07.960
and shoot me dead.

21:08.310 --> 21:09.240
I will thank you.

21:09.400 --> 21:10.830
Really.

21:18.640 --> 21:20.100
I know Zhou Jin's marriage

21:20.470 --> 21:21.930
makes you uncomfortable.

21:22.680 --> 21:24.610
But you are not a teenager anymore.

21:25.330 --> 21:27.240
This is the critical moment
of the planned round-up.

21:27.240 --> 21:28.680
You can't mess it up

21:28.840 --> 21:29.420
just because of Zhou Jin.

21:29.420 --> 21:30.550
Zhou Chuan died!

21:31.290 --> 21:33.290
That's why I volunteered to do this.

21:42.510 --> 21:44.240
You were right about one thing.

21:45.160 --> 21:47.560
If someone wants to accomplish something,

21:48.200 --> 21:49.640
he must have faith.

21:50.640 --> 21:51.270
This is

21:52.070 --> 21:53.270
my faith.

21:55.680 --> 21:56.510
Are you sure?

21:56.330 --> 22:03.330
[2012]

21:57.070 --> 21:57.830
Yes.

21:59.310 --> 22:01.110
I only have two requests for you.

22:01.240 --> 22:01.880
First,

22:02.270 --> 22:03.730
stay firm with your faith.

22:03.790 --> 22:04.350
Second,

22:05.110 --> 22:05.770
stay alive.

22:06.270 --> 22:06.790
Yes.

22:07.270 --> 22:09.200
I promise to complete the mission.

22:12.680 --> 22:13.310
I

22:15.160 --> 22:17.360
can't let my family shed tears anymore.

22:56.030 --> 22:57.830
Isn't this a gift from Zhou?

23:12.400 --> 23:13.240
Don't forget.

23:14.360 --> 23:17.250
Even if everything has changed
in the past five years,

23:17.250 --> 23:18.400
you're still a cop.

23:31.230 --> 23:31.880
Watch out!

23:42.480 --> 23:43.270
Xiao Mao?

23:44.820 --> 23:45.450
Cheng.

23:46.790 --> 23:48.320
Didn't you stop being a cop?

23:48.610 --> 23:49.740
If Boss He finds out,

23:50.110 --> 23:51.400
you'll be dead meat.

23:51.880 --> 23:53.410
Did he tell you to follow me?

23:54.680 --> 23:55.240
Speak!

23:57.720 --> 23:58.280
Yes.

24:01.070 --> 24:01.640
Cheng,

24:02.200 --> 24:03.200
can you let me go?

24:03.680 --> 24:04.830
I didn't see anything.

24:04.830 --> 24:06.000
I didn't see anything.

24:06.000 --> 24:07.000
Let me go, please.

24:07.640 --> 24:08.550
Turn yourself in,

24:08.550 --> 24:09.240
right now.

24:09.640 --> 24:10.500
I can't, Cheng.

24:10.960 --> 24:12.960
Turning myself in means killing me.

24:13.510 --> 24:14.110
Let me go.

24:14.640 --> 24:15.700
I won't say anything.

24:15.700 --> 24:16.590
Not a word.

24:16.920 --> 24:17.400
Cheng.

24:17.400 --> 24:18.110
Xiao Mao,

24:18.550 --> 24:19.410
don't force me.

24:19.750 --> 24:22.550
I've treated you like
my brother for so many years.

24:23.160 --> 24:23.680
Or,

24:24.680 --> 24:26.680
don't you think about your brother?

24:28.720 --> 24:29.350
Okay.

24:30.720 --> 24:31.240
Cheng,

24:32.510 --> 24:33.570
I'll listen to you.

24:34.920 --> 24:36.050
I'll turn myself in.

24:37.050 --> 24:38.180
I won't say a word.

24:38.680 --> 24:39.810
I'll turn myself in.

24:44.310 --> 24:44.960
Cheng,

24:45.310 --> 24:46.170
don't blame me.

24:46.480 --> 24:47.920
You brought this on yourself.
You're a cop.

24:47.920 --> 24:48.950
It's either you or me.

24:48.950 --> 24:49.880
I have no choice.

25:15.110 --> 25:15.840
Jiang Cheng,

25:16.110 --> 25:16.880
let go.

25:17.310 --> 25:18.110
Let go!

25:27.110 --> 25:28.680
Don't worry, he won't die.

25:29.880 --> 25:31.400
Can you be more careful?

25:31.750 --> 25:33.150
Did you bring handcuffs?

25:38.920 --> 25:40.350
I was always curious before.

25:40.350 --> 25:41.240
Every time you see me,

25:41.240 --> 25:42.300
did you bring them?

25:42.590 --> 25:43.880
Cut the crap, hurry up.

25:56.480 --> 25:57.960
I'll leave the rest to you.

25:59.000 --> 26:01.030
Didn't you say you could
handle your subordinates?

26:01.030 --> 26:02.020
You were careless?

26:02.020 --> 26:02.500
So,

26:02.530 --> 26:03.860
what other tricks do you have
to win people over?

26:03.860 --> 26:04.860
Teach me quickly.

26:05.440 --> 26:07.200
Is Dahua reliable?

26:07.880 --> 26:09.540
Dahua is different from them.

26:09.800 --> 26:10.990
He's an orphan,

26:11.010 --> 26:12.720
and only needs to feed himself.

26:12.720 --> 26:14.000
He has no weaknesses

26:14.160 --> 26:15.560
and no blood on his hands.

26:15.820 --> 26:16.880
He's kind at heart.

26:17.970 --> 26:20.210
Two years ago, Lai San forced him
to stab someone.

26:20.210 --> 26:21.070
But Dahua would rather jump
into the river,

26:21.070 --> 26:21.920
than doing so.

26:22.790 --> 26:25.190
He seems to consider you
his savior, right?

26:26.000 --> 26:27.240
He was so naive,

26:27.240 --> 26:28.240
so I brought him along.

26:28.240 --> 26:30.040
Otherwise, he might get killed.

26:30.480 --> 26:32.480
Dahua knows this very well himself.

26:36.640 --> 26:38.040
Then how will you go back?

26:38.960 --> 26:39.960
What else can I do?

26:40.830 --> 26:41.680
Wish me luck.

26:42.160 --> 26:42.890
Jiang Cheng!

26:43.830 --> 26:44.560
I know.

26:45.070 --> 26:46.790
One wrong step will kill me.

26:47.590 --> 26:48.350
Don't worry.

26:49.000 --> 26:50.400
I want to come back alive.

26:50.860 --> 26:51.990
Until I contact you,

26:52.480 --> 26:53.540
we should not meet.

26:57.400 --> 26:58.550
If I die,

26:58.550 --> 26:59.720
collect my body.

27:14.920 --> 27:17.050
That's Professor Jiang's car, right?

27:19.100 --> 27:20.770
Yes, Professor Jiang.

27:30.220 --> 27:30.880
Oh my.

27:33.720 --> 27:35.720
Why did it rain so heavily
all of a sudden?

27:35.720 --> 27:36.980
Don't you have a class?

27:37.030 --> 27:38.790
It's fine. I have time,

27:39.480 --> 27:40.480
and this case…

27:40.480 --> 27:41.000
Senior.

27:42.480 --> 27:43.080
Umbrella.

27:45.400 --> 27:46.000
Well, if you told me earlier

27:46.000 --> 27:47.860
that Professor Jiang
was dropping you off,

27:47.860 --> 27:49.480
I wouldn't have come down to pick you up.

27:49.480 --> 27:50.660
In the past, you could chase a petty thief

27:50.660 --> 27:51.740
for eight blocks.

27:51.830 --> 27:53.200
Now that you're married,

27:53.200 --> 27:54.420
you can't even open a car door

27:54.420 --> 27:55.550
or hold an umbrella.

27:56.960 --> 27:57.680
Why do you talk so much?

27:57.680 --> 27:58.790
Professor Jiang, control your wife.

27:58.790 --> 28:00.590
She's bullying the vulnerable.

28:00.790 --> 28:01.400
Sorry.

28:02.000 --> 28:04.260
I'm afraid I'm one of the vulnerable too.

28:05.000 --> 28:05.480
See?

28:05.870 --> 28:06.590
Fine.

28:06.880 --> 28:08.030
I've had enough of your romantic behavior.

28:08.030 --> 28:08.760
I'm leaving.

28:10.310 --> 28:10.840
Let's go.

28:14.070 --> 28:15.330
What do you want to know

28:15.720 --> 28:17.400
about this case?

28:18.030 --> 28:19.680
Regarding Zhao Xiaoyu's case,

28:19.680 --> 28:21.280
I'd like to ask your opinion.

28:21.440 --> 28:23.200
Are you really asking for my opinion?

28:23.200 --> 28:23.960
The way you ask

28:23.960 --> 28:25.310
is like my high school teacher

28:25.310 --> 28:26.720
making me recite a text.

28:27.790 --> 28:30.590
I genuinely want to seek advice
from Officer Zhou.

28:30.970 --> 28:32.110
When you were in high school,

28:32.110 --> 28:33.340
did you dislike reciting texts?

28:33.340 --> 28:34.620
Of course.

28:35.450 --> 28:36.850
A top student like you

28:36.870 --> 28:38.600
cannot understand a poor student's pain.

28:38.600 --> 28:40.680
When I was in school,
I even went to tutoring.

28:40.680 --> 28:42.160
The tutor I found

28:42.180 --> 28:43.340
was my mom's classmate,

28:43.340 --> 28:44.410
a total tyrant.

28:44.550 --> 28:45.750
If I recited wrong,

28:46.090 --> 28:48.550
she would hit my palms
with a remote control.

28:49.030 --> 28:49.480
Did it hurt?

28:49.480 --> 28:50.550
Of course it did.

28:50.830 --> 28:52.480
She said pain could teach me a lesson.

28:52.480 --> 28:53.360
You're much better.

28:53.360 --> 28:55.030
Your students must be very happy.

28:55.030 --> 28:57.230
If you had been in Zhizi Alley back then,

28:57.550 --> 28:59.310
I definitely would have
asked you for tutoring.

28:59.310 --> 28:59.880
Zhou Jin.

29:00.410 --> 29:00.900
Here.

29:00.670 --> 29:03.800
♪ I should never have let you bear this ♪

29:07.630 --> 29:11.640
♪ I always want to give you
everything I have ♪

29:08.440 --> 29:09.040
Hansheng.

29:10.160 --> 29:10.760
What's up?

29:11.830 --> 29:12.400
Let's go.

29:12.550 --> 29:14.480
I have some new ideas for you today.

29:15.040 --> 29:18.760
♪ If only it could win your heart,
even for a moment ♪

29:19.340 --> 29:22.410
♪ Look at the fish
swimming in the ocean depths ♪

29:24.340 --> 29:26.560
♪ They're so free ♪

29:28.810 --> 29:31.880
♪ How can I tell you ♪

29:31.900 --> 29:35.530
♪ How much I love you with a smile ♪

29:36.200 --> 29:39.030
♪ I am sure to ♪

29:39.060 --> 29:42.610
♪ Walk with you ♪

29:43.630 --> 29:47.110
♪ I look at you day and night ♪

29:47.130 --> 29:51.260
♪ One more glance is not enough ♪

29:51.280 --> 29:53.500
♪ At the crossroad ♪

29:53.530 --> 29:56.900
♪ To the left or right ♪

29:57.900 --> 30:01.820
♪ I want to hold your hand ♪

30:15.200 --> 30:15.830
You two take a look.

30:15.830 --> 30:17.830
I'll keep checking the statements.

30:22.750 --> 30:24.550
They were sitting here that day.

30:25.820 --> 30:27.180
Zhao Xiaoyu was

30:27.210 --> 30:28.340
sitting right here.

30:38.620 --> 30:39.950
What are your thoughts?

30:40.590 --> 30:42.650
We can do the crime scene simulation,

30:42.880 --> 30:44.270
a compulsory course at the police academy.

30:44.270 --> 30:45.830
I can put myself in Zhao Xiaoyu's shoes

30:45.830 --> 30:48.690
and reenact the encounter
with the killer that day.

30:48.690 --> 30:50.000
Do you remember the witness statements?

30:50.000 --> 30:50.600
Of course.

30:51.240 --> 30:51.720
Okay.

30:52.110 --> 30:53.910
Let's start the simulation now.

31:03.160 --> 31:04.020
You observe me.

31:04.160 --> 31:06.070
Stop me if there's any problem.

31:06.310 --> 31:06.680
Okay.

31:07.480 --> 31:08.340
Take your time.

31:36.640 --> 31:37.400
Xiaoyu,

31:39.460 --> 31:41.110
let's have another drink.

31:59.900 --> 32:00.740
Xi,

32:02.110 --> 32:03.310
I'm not feeling well.

32:03.670 --> 32:04.830
I want to get some fresh air.

32:04.830 --> 32:06.530
What's wrong? Are you okay?

32:06.750 --> 32:07.590
I'm fine.

32:08.110 --> 32:09.640
Can you manage by yourself?

32:09.860 --> 32:10.650
Don't worry.

32:11.570 --> 32:13.060
Xi, let's have a drink.

32:13.270 --> 32:13.960
Okay.

32:29.760 --> 32:31.110
Hey, gorgeous.

32:31.750 --> 32:32.680
Have a drink.

33:30.140 --> 33:30.990
Are you okay?

33:49.030 --> 33:50.590
Come with me.

33:54.350 --> 33:55.400
Now?

33:59.110 --> 34:00.370
What are you afraid of?

34:15.400 --> 34:16.960
This killer is so bold.

34:17.480 --> 34:18.679
In this environment,

34:19.110 --> 34:20.190
he blatantly

34:20.210 --> 34:21.469
took Zhao Xiaoyu away.

34:22.110 --> 34:23.230
Any new thoughts?

34:24.110 --> 34:25.370
This is a provocation.

34:28.800 --> 34:29.710
A copycat

34:30.400 --> 34:31.440
usually takes

34:31.880 --> 34:33.070
his relative,

34:33.400 --> 34:34.110
his friend,

34:34.760 --> 34:36.290
or his admirer as the model.

34:36.880 --> 34:39.480
As for the killer of
the Huaiguang Case, Qi Yan,

34:39.630 --> 34:40.360
did the task force

34:40.360 --> 34:41.800
check his family background

34:41.800 --> 34:43.130
or social connections?

34:43.360 --> 34:43.960
Of course.

34:44.400 --> 34:45.600
But we found nothing.

34:45.760 --> 34:46.960
We only know his name?

34:49.800 --> 34:50.960
Before he showed up,

34:51.510 --> 34:53.550
we had nothing but a profile

34:53.840 --> 34:54.880
and his DNA.

34:55.840 --> 34:57.110
I only knew his name

34:57.540 --> 34:59.790
when he told us.

35:01.590 --> 35:03.760
The task force, according to this name,

35:03.760 --> 35:06.320
along with my descriptions
and profiling report,

35:06.320 --> 35:07.880
deployed a large number
of grass-roots police forces

35:07.880 --> 35:09.760
to conduct interviews and investigations

35:09.760 --> 35:11.670
to further verify his identity.

35:12.590 --> 35:14.110
But it all came to nothing.

35:15.400 --> 35:16.480
Crime Research Lab

35:16.480 --> 35:17.230
intended to use Qi Yan

35:17.230 --> 35:18.760
as a typical case study.

35:19.760 --> 35:21.150
However, the lack of his family background

35:21.150 --> 35:22.590
and personal experience

35:22.840 --> 35:25.370
prevented this project
from moving forward.

35:28.840 --> 35:29.960
Is it possible

35:31.070 --> 35:32.800
that Qi Yan isn't his real name?

35:34.590 --> 35:36.630
He didn't plan on letting me return alive.

35:36.630 --> 35:37.440
There was no need to lie

35:37.440 --> 35:38.840
to a dying man.

35:43.440 --> 35:44.280
Let's go back.

35:49.070 --> 35:50.730
But there's one more question

35:51.230 --> 35:52.560
that I can't figure out.

35:53.590 --> 35:54.110
Tell me.

35:56.280 --> 35:57.880
Usually, copycat crimes are

35:58.150 --> 36:00.000
committed due to a lack of creativity

36:00.000 --> 36:01.330
or a lack of experience.

36:01.920 --> 36:03.920
That's why they need to copy others.

36:05.070 --> 36:07.030
And the results are often clumsy.

36:08.440 --> 36:09.970
But the person we're facing

36:10.800 --> 36:12.630
calmly altered a dress,

36:13.150 --> 36:15.030
carefully tied a bow,

36:15.760 --> 36:17.110
and even deliberately

36:17.150 --> 36:18.950
showed off new criminal markers

36:19.360 --> 36:20.960
to flaunt his achievements.

36:22.280 --> 36:22.960
But

36:23.590 --> 36:25.190
it's not the 90s anymore.

36:26.010 --> 36:27.610
He's even bolder than Qi Yan.

36:42.360 --> 36:43.110
You mean

36:43.960 --> 36:45.890
he's an advanced version of Qi Yan.

36:46.320 --> 36:46.920
Yes.

37:13.670 --> 37:14.270
It's fine.

37:18.000 --> 37:18.880
Let's go home,

37:18.900 --> 37:20.700
not going back to the team today.

37:25.550 --> 37:26.480
Let me drive.

37:27.630 --> 37:29.510
You didn't rest well last night either.

37:29.510 --> 37:30.640
Take a nap in the car.

37:35.110 --> 37:35.760
Get in.

37:58.400 --> 37:59.600
Buckle the beat belt.

38:14.800 --> 38:15.230
Adjust the seat back

38:15.230 --> 38:16.760
to a comfortable position.

38:26.670 --> 38:27.400
Go to sleep.

38:32.030 --> 38:32.960
Close your eyes.

38:50.460 --> 38:51.140
Go home.

39:15.150 --> 39:16.080
Jiang Hansheng.

39:16.320 --> 39:16.980
Jiang Hansheng.

39:16.980 --> 39:17.910
Jiang Hansheng.

39:17.920 --> 39:18.880
Jiang Hansheng.

39:19.030 --> 39:19.920
Jiang Hansheng.

39:19.920 --> 39:20.660
Jiang Hansheng.

39:20.660 --> 39:21.970
Jiang Hansheng.

39:22.100 --> 39:22.840
Jiang Hansheng.

39:22.840 --> 39:23.320
Jiang Hansheng.

39:23.320 --> 39:24.190
Jiang Hansheng.

39:24.190 --> 39:24.960
Jiang Hansheng.

39:24.960 --> 39:25.550
Jiang Hansheng.

39:25.550 --> 39:26.550
Jiang Hansheng.

39:26.630 --> 39:27.280
Jiang Hansheng.

39:27.280 --> 39:28.000
Jiang Hansheng.

39:28.000 --> 39:28.930
Jiang Hansheng.

39:29.590 --> 39:30.520
Jiang Hansheng.

39:31.400 --> 39:32.330
Jiang Hansheng.

39:33.000 --> 39:33.930
Jiang Hansheng.

39:37.110 --> 39:38.040
Jiang Hansheng.

39:38.230 --> 39:39.160
Jiang Hansheng.

39:40.090 --> 39:41.050
Jiang Hansheng.

39:41.760 --> 39:42.590
Jiang Hansheng.

39:42.590 --> 39:43.520
Jiang Hansheng.

39:44.590 --> 39:45.520
Jiang Hansheng.

39:45.880 --> 39:46.810
Jiang Hansheng.

39:47.890 --> 39:48.820
Jiang Hansheng.

40:14.860 --> 40:20.220
[2009]

40:55.030 --> 40:55.960
Jiang Hansheng.

40:56.440 --> 40:58.440
You are here for Zhou Jin, right?

41:01.710 --> 41:03.750
I remember when you were little,

41:03.880 --> 41:05.710
you were just as quiet as you are now.

41:05.710 --> 41:06.570
I've graduated

41:07.000 --> 41:08.710
from the Public Security University.

41:08.710 --> 41:10.550
Really? Congratulations.

41:10.910 --> 41:12.740
I also graduated from
the Public Security University.

41:12.740 --> 41:13.660
So,

41:14.050 --> 41:15.160
we're alumni.

41:15.430 --> 41:16.780
If you need anything,

41:16.810 --> 41:17.740
just let me know.

41:18.880 --> 41:19.530
Thank you.

41:23.110 --> 41:23.840
Can I

41:24.320 --> 41:25.550
meet with Zhou Jin?

41:25.840 --> 41:26.700
She is not home.

41:28.160 --> 41:28.960
I just...

41:28.990 --> 41:29.960
I know.

41:30.390 --> 41:31.750
Don't be nervous.

41:32.010 --> 41:32.780
Or you'd look like a man

41:32.780 --> 41:34.470
visiting his in-laws.

41:34.780 --> 41:36.410
Come, have some water.

41:36.630 --> 41:37.280
Thank you.

41:40.070 --> 41:41.400
Let me put it this way.

41:42.240 --> 41:43.360
You might not

41:43.510 --> 41:44.590
know her well.

41:45.280 --> 41:46.400
Jin

41:47.230 --> 41:48.510
looks smart,

41:49.800 --> 41:51.530
but she's actually a bit naive.

41:52.400 --> 41:53.660
She's single-minded.

41:54.510 --> 41:55.440
If she

41:56.110 --> 41:57.960
falls in love with someone,

41:58.360 --> 42:00.090
she can't think of anyone else.

42:01.940 --> 42:04.170
If I'm not mistaken,

42:04.230 --> 42:05.840
you might be disappointed.

42:08.440 --> 42:10.210
I'm sorry. I was being presumptuous.

42:10.210 --> 42:10.890
No.

42:11.830 --> 42:13.270
You are so young.

42:13.340 --> 42:15.200
Why do you speak like an old fogey?

42:18.670 --> 42:19.670
I wonder why Jin is

42:19.770 --> 42:21.330
so charming for you.

42:38.150 --> 42:39.950
I shouldn't bother you anymore.

42:40.580 --> 42:41.910
Hansheng, you just

42:41.940 --> 42:43.320
graduated and haven't made any money.

42:43.320 --> 42:44.480
Take this.

42:44.670 --> 42:45.530
Please keep it.

42:46.280 --> 42:47.940
I just want to thank Uncle Zhou

42:48.070 --> 42:48.710
and your family

42:48.710 --> 42:49.910
for taking care of me.

42:50.190 --> 42:51.790
No need. Come visit us often.

42:51.960 --> 42:52.760
Take it.

42:53.010 --> 42:54.590
Don't tell Zhou Jin I was here.

42:54.590 --> 42:56.120
I don't want to disturb her.

42:58.360 --> 42:59.290
I'm leaving now.

43:04.710 --> 43:05.510
Hansheng.
